{197}{}{我想问你一件事。 -- I would like to ask you something.}
#{198}{}{...and once again, diverge.}
{198}{}{……再一次，分道扬镳。 -- ...and once again, diverge.}
#{199}{}{Shh! Now is not the time to talk, wanderer. I must complete my daily ritual.}
{199}{}{嘘！现在不是谈话的时候，流浪者。我必须完成每天的例行公事。 -- Shh! Now is not the time to talk, wanderer. I must complete my daily ritual.}
#{200}{}{Some other time then.}
{200}{}{那就改天吧。 -- Some other time then.}
#{201}{}{I have never seen anything like this - a child of the Devourer, helping people like us. You give me much to think about, wanderer.}
{201}{}{我从没见过这样的事――一个吞食者的孩子，帮助我们这样的人。你让我想的太多了，流浪汉。 -- I have never seen anything like this - a child of the Devourer, helping people like us. You give me much to think about, wanderer.}
#{202}{}{Everyone! Our hero returns!}
{202}{}{所有人！我们的英雄回来了！ -- Everyone! Our hero returns!}
#{203}{}{Our paths cross again. What will this bring today?}
{203}{}{我们的路又交叉了。今天会带来什么？ -- Our paths cross again. What will this bring today?}
#{204}{}{I should go. Take care.}
{204}{}{我该走了。当心。 -- I should go. Take care.}
#{205}{}{Do you know? The raiders are no more!}
{205}{}{你知道吗？掠夺者不在了！ -- Do you know? The raiders are no more!}
