{215}{}{消息传遍了整个荒地！谢谢您！我终于为我的最后一次旅程做好了准备，那时我将走向我所爱的人的灵魂，把部落留给年轻人。 -- Word of it is spreading throughout the wasteland! Thank you! I am finally ready for my final journey, when I will go to the spirits of my loved ones and leave the tribe to the young.}
